{"id": "zur1665702620176", "title": "Binding Web Layout to Component Structure", "breadcrumbs": ["Developing Web Applications", "Server Page Components", "Binding Web Layout to Component Structure"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zur1665702620176.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">Binding Web Layout to Component Structure</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous:   Presentation-Logic Split for Server Pages \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous:   Presentation-Logic Split for Server Pages \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eub1665702756707.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:   External Web Layout Definitions \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:   External Web Layout Definitions \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/brz1665702626759.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/zur1665702620176.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/zur1665702620176.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/zur1665702620176.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534627\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534627\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 13, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zur1665702620176.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zur1665702620176.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zur1665702620176.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zur1665702620176\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Binding Web Layout to Component Structure\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"zur1665702620176__binding_web_layout_to_component_structure_68317\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Binding refers to the way in which layout elements are connected to data structures and triggers in the component structure. It ensures that data is displayed by the appropriate HTML elements in the web page, and that the correct trigger is executed when data in a field is changed.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zur1665702620176__p_d20099e1_d20100e1_d20101e1\">Uniface web applications make use of <dfn class=\"term\">late binding</dfn>, meaning that the connection between the component structure and HTML element is only established at runtime. However, the binding must be defined in the web layout definition, used to generate the runtime web page, and this does not happen automatically. Thus, if you add a field that needs to be available in the generated web page to the component structure, you must also add it to the web layout with the required binding information.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zur1665702620176__topic_d14452e1_d14453e1_d14454e1_d14455e1_d14456e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1066222e59\">\n                  \n Binding for Dynamic Server Pages\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zur1665702620176__p_d20105e1_d20106e1_d20107e1\">For dynamic server pages, the binding information is defined by the <code class=\"ph codeph\">id</code> attribute for the bound HTML element, such as , <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;div&gt;</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;tr&gt;</code>. The <code class=\"ph codeph\">id</code> attribute is completely standards-compliant, so it does not pose a problem for XHTML editors.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2183e1_d2184e1_d2185e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">DSP Binding</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2183e1_d2184e1_d2185e1__entry__1\">\n Component Object\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2183e1_d2184e1_d2185e1__entry__2\">\n Binding Attribute Syntax\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2183e1_d2184e1_d2185e1__entry__1\">\n Entity\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2183e1_d2184e1_d2185e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">id=\"uent:<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>\"</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2183e1_d2184e1_d2185e1__entry__1\">\n Occurrence\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2183e1_d2184e1_d2185e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">id=\"uocc:<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>\"</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Or:</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">id=\"uocs:<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>\"</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">id=\"uoce:<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>\"</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2183e1_d2184e1_d2185e1__entry__1\">\n Field\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2183e1_d2184e1_d2185e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">id=\"ufld:<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>\"</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2183e1_d2184e1_d2185e1__entry__1\">\n Label\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2183e1_d2184e1_d2185e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">id=\"ulbl:<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>\"</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zur1665702620176__p_d20108e1_d20109e1_d20110e1\">For example, the following input element is bound to the SHIPTO field of the CUST_ORDER.SALES entity:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;input id=\"ufld:SHIPTO.CUST_ORDER.SALES\" value=\"Input Element\"/&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zur1665702620176__p_d20111e1_d20112e1_d20113e1\">Occurrences can be bound to a single element, or they can be bound to a range of elements. This can be useful in an HTML table where each occurrence occupies a fixed number of rows. The first of these rows would be a <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;tr&gt;</code> element bound using the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uocs:</code> prefix, and the last of them using the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uoce:</code> prefix.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"zur1665702620176__fig_d20117e1_d20118e1_d20119e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>DSP web layout showing ID-based binding</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"HTML layout of DSP component\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/dsp_htmlcode.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zur1665702620176__topic_d14457e1_d14458e1_d14459e1_d14460e1_d14461e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1066222e254\">\n                  \n Binding for Static Server pages\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zur1665702620176__p_d20126e1_d20127e1_d20128e1\">For static server pages, binding information is provided in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">name</code> attribute of Uniface-specific XHTML tags such as <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-subst&gt;</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-occurrence&gt;</code>. The use of Uniface-specific tags makes it more difficult to use a standard XHTML editor, because it will not recognize these tags.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2186e1_d2187e1_d2188e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Static Server Page Binding</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2186e1_d2187e1_d2188e1__entry__1\">\n Component Object\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2186e1_d2187e1_d2188e1__entry__2\">\n Binding Attribute Syntax\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2186e1_d2187e1_d2188e1__entry__1\">\n Entity\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2186e1_d2187e1_d2188e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-entity name=\"<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>\"&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2186e1_d2187e1_d2188e1__entry__1\">\n Occurrence\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2186e1_d2187e1_d2188e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-occurrence name=\"<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>\"&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2186e1_d2187e1_d2188e1__entry__1\">\n Field\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2186e1_d2187e1_d2188e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-subst type=\"text\" name=\"<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>\" sync=\"1\"&gt;\n &lt;input name=\"<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>\" value=\"Input\" type=\"text\" /&gt;\n &lt;/x-subst&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2186e1_d2187e1_d2188e1__entry__1\">\n Label\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zur1665702620176__table_d2186e1_d2187e1_d2188e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-subst type=\"label\" name=\"<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>\"&gt;\n &lt;label&gt;<var class=\"keyword varname\">Label</var>&lt;/label&gt;\n &lt;/x-subst&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"p\" id=\"zur1665702620176__p_d20129e1_d20130e1_d20131e1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"zur1665702620176__fig_w953ab1b5b7b7b1_w954ab1b5b7b7_w955ab1b5b7_w956ab1b5_w957ab1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 2. </span>USP web layout showing name-based binding </figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Binding in web layout of static server page\" aria-label=\"Open image in gallery mode\" class=\"image expandable\" data-fancy=\"gallery\" data-gallery=\"gallery\" data-remote=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/usp_web_layout.png?_LANG=enus\" data-title=\"Figure 2. USP web layout showing name-based binding \" role=\"button\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/usp_web_layout.png?_LANG=enus\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" tabindex=\"0\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534627\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534627\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Binding Web Layout to Component Structure Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Binding Web Layout to Component Structure Binding refers to the way in which layout elements are connected to data structures and triggers in the component structure. It ensures that data is displayed by the appropriate HTML elements in the web page, and that the correct trigger is executed when data in a field is changed. Uniface web applications make use of late binding , meaning that the connection between the component structure and HTML element is only established at runtime. However, the binding must be defined in the web layout definition, used to generate the runtime web page, and this does not happen automatically. Thus, if you add a field that needs to be available in the generated web page to the component structure, you must also add it to the web layout with the required binding information. Binding for Dynamic Server Pages For dynamic server pages, the binding information is defined by the id attribute for the bound HTML element, such as , <div> or <tr> . The id attribute is completely standards-compliant, so it does not pose a problem for XHTML editors. Table 1. DSP Binding Component Object Binding Attribute Syntax Entity id=\"uent: Entity . Model \" Occurrence id=\"uocc: Entity . Model \" Or: id=\"uocs: Entity . Model \" id=\"uoce: Entity . Model \" Field id=\"ufld: Field . Entity . Model \" Label id=\"ulbl: Field . Entity . Model \" For example, the following input element is bound to the SHIPTO field of the CUST_ORDER.SALES entity: <input id=\"ufld:SHIPTO.CUST_ORDER.SALES\" value=\"Input Element\"/> Copy Occurrences can be bound to a single element, or they can be bound to a range of elements. This can be useful in an HTML table where each occurrence occupies a fixed number of rows. The first of these rows would be a <tr> element bound using the uocs: prefix, and the last of them using the uoce: prefix. Figure 1. DSP web layout showing ID-based binding Binding for Static Server pages For static server pages, binding information is provided in the name attribute of Uniface-specific XHTML tags such as <x-subst> and <x-occurrence> . The use of Uniface-specific tags makes it more difficult to use a standard XHTML editor, because it will not recognize these tags. Table 2. Static Server Page Binding Component Object Binding Attribute Syntax Entity <x-entity name=\" Entity . Model \"> Occurrence <x-occurrence name=\" Entity . Model \"> Field <x-subst type=\"text\" name=\" Field . Entity . Model \" sync=\"1\"> <input name=\" Field . Entity . Model \" value=\"Input\" type=\"text\" /> </x-subst> Label <x-subst type=\"label\" name=\" Field . Entity . Model \"> <label> Label </label> </x-subst> Figure 2. USP web layout showing name-based binding Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}